My Notes

CHELSEA'S DANDY DUPLEX w/FIREPLACE
PHOTOS AND VIDEO COMING SOON. Supremely located and superbly unique, this spacious, rare, dandy duplex with wood-burning fireplace is a stand out residence for all the right reasons - a home with good space and great character. Offering two sizeable bedrooms and two full baths - and sporting soaring 10-foot ceilings and a homey upstairs/downstairs lifestyle, this inviting residence feels like a real home. Upstairs is the lofty living room with its big windows and its wonderful working fireplace. This is the entertaining floor and offers an open dining foyer, a big, practical kitchen with dishwasher and ample counter and cabinet space, and a full guest bath. Down the straight-stairway is a jumbo den/media/office/workout area - a flexible gateway to the king-sized master bedroom and the sizeable guest bedroom - both served by a full bath and a sauna. Sweetly situated in an historic building, this delightful, pet-friendly residence -- with central AC and a prime Chelsea location that comes with bragging rights -- offers sublime proximity to downtown's most coveted shopping, dining, and cultural destinations - not to mention a plethora of easy transportation options. Big, practical, unique and convenient - your dandy duplex awaits.…  More Less
